sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Platform Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as llama-stack-k8s-operator<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Pipeline<br/>(in-process)
    participant Server as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Server: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution CR Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (CR created/updated)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>Kustomize: Render manifests from base templates<br/>(Deployment, Service, SA, PVC, NP, CRB)
    Kustomize-->>Operator: Transformed Kubernetes resources<br/>(name-prefixed, namespace-injected, fields-mutated)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply rendered resources<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources created/updated
    Operator->>Server: GET /v1/health<br/>HTTP (no auth)
    Server-->>Operator: Health status
    Operator->>Server: GET /v1/providers<br/>HTTP (no auth)
    Server-->>Operator: Provider info
    Operator->>Server: GET /v1/version<br/>HTTP (no auth)
    Server-->>Operator: Version info
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update CR status with health/provider/version<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,Server: Flow 2: ConfigMap Change Detection

    User->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap (user-config or CA bundle)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (ConfigMap changed)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Lookup referencing LlamaStackDistributions<br/>(field indexer query)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Matching LlamaStackDistribution CRs
    Operator->>Operator: Recalculate content-based hash
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update Deployment pod template annotations<br/>(triggers rolling restart)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Deployment updated
